title: 'Eternals' Preview, the 'Station Eleven' Trailer, and 'Love Life' Season 2
description:
Ahead of the premiere of 'Eternals,' Chris and Andy talk about where the movie might lead the Marvel franchise (7:32). Plus, 'Station Eleven' might be the only pandemic show we're willing to watch (40:32) and the first two episodes of 'Love Life' Season 2 are a delight (43:21).

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald
Producer: Kaya McMullen
